OL,3,CFresh appeal for information over
OL,4,CMarian Beattie's murder 53 years ago
OL,6,FA fresh appeal for information has
OL,7,Fbeen made over the murder of a teenage
OL,8,Fgirl in Co Tyrone 53 years ago.
OL,10,FMarian Beattie, 18, was last seen
OL,11,Falive at a charity dance at Hadden's
OL,12,FGarage in Aughnacloy on March 30, 1973.
OL,14,FHer body was found at the bottom of a
OL,15,Fquarry early the next morning.
OL,17,FExactly 53 years on, police have
OL,18,Fissued a new appeal for information
OL,19,Ffrom the public.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
