FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774991532
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information over
OL,4,CMarian Beattie's murder 53 years ago
OL,6,FThey said she was at the dance to
OL,7,Flisten to her brother's band, and was
OL,8,Fseen leaving with a young man just
OL,9,Fafter 1am, walking in the direction of
OL,10,FHadden's Quarry.
OL,12,FOfficers have asked to hear from
OL,13,Fanyone who remembers seeing Ms Beattie
OL,14,Fat the event or leaving it.
OL,16,F"We believe Marian left the dance at
OL,17,FHadden's Garage with a man, walking in
OL,18,Fthe direction of the nearby car park
OL,19,Fat the top of Hadden's Quarry about
OL,20,F400 yards away from the garage," a
OL,21,Fpolice spokesperson said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774991532
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information over
OL,4,CMarian Beattie's murder 53 years ago
OL,6,F"We do not know what happened next but
OL,7,FMarian's body was found at the bottom
OL,8,Fof the quarry below the car park.
OL,10,F"I appreciate this murder took place
OL,11,Fover 50 years ago but we would like to
OL,12,Ftalk to anyone who was at the dance at
OL,13,FHadden's Garage on the night of Friday
OL,14,F30 March 1973.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
