OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774991532
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information over
OL,4,CMarian Beattie's murder 53 years ago
OL,6,F"Marian went there with a girlfriend
OL,7,Fto listen to her brother's band. Did
OL,8,Fyou see who she was dancing with or
OL,9,Fspeaking with? Did you see her leave
OL,10,Fthe dance with a man? Do you know who
OL,11,Fhe was? Did you see her in the car
OL,12,Fpark at the quarry any time after
OL,13,F1.15am on the Saturday morning?
OL,15,F"Additionally, do you remember anyone
OL,16,Fwho was at the dance returning home
OL,17,Fdistressed or with dirt on their
OL,18,Fclothes? Has anyone ever talked about
OL,19,Fthe events of that night?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
