CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774991532
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information over
OL,4,CMarian Beattie's murder 53 years ago
OL,6,FThe police spokesperson said Ms
OL,7,FBeattie's family deserve to know what
OL,8,Fhappened that night.
OL,10,F"I am appealing to anyone who may be
OL,11,Fable to help us progress the
OL,12,Finvestigation and bring some closure
OL,13,Fto the Beattie family to come forward
OL,14,Fand speak to detectives in Legacy
OL,15,FInvestigation Branch," they said.
